There is no such thing as "the" price of Bitcoin. 

Public orderbooks:
- bids/asks 
- last trades
- weighed averages
- indexes
Different rates for:
- payment processors
- online buy (direct OTC, P2P)
- cash/ATMs
- large bank OTC
- friends

The price is whatever you accept to pay.
